\item Find Jason's average speed, in kilometres per hour, from Town A to Town B.

\AnswerLine[][km/h]
\Marks{1}

\item Jason leaves Town C at 12\,00.

Jason continues to Town D at a constant speed of 15 kilometres per hour.

\begin{subparts}
\item Calculate the time Jason takes to travel from Town C to Town D.

Give your answer in hours and minutes.

\hfill \AnswerLineShort[][] h \AnswerLineShort[][] min
\Marks{2}

